  "prompt": "If I stop chasing my crush will he start chasing me back?",
  "response": "While there's no guaranteed outcome in relationships, the idea that someone might become more interested if you stop pursuing them is rooted in the psychology of attraction. Sometimes, stepping back can create a sense of mystery and allow the other person to reflect on their feelings. \n\nHowever, it's important to remember that everyone is different. Some may realize they have feelings when they see less of you, while others might not feel the same way regardless. The key is to focus on your own well-being and balance your emotions while respecting their space. Be yourself, and if it\u2019s meant to be, it will unfold naturally.",
